    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>What's wrong with casting primitives?</p>\n\n<p>If you don't want to cast for some reason, you could do</p>\n\n<pre><code>double d = num * 1.0 / denom;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
