    "question_id" : 3144610,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>use something like:</p>\n\n<pre><code>double step = 1d / 5;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>(1d is a cast to double)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
