    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Best way to do this is</p>\n\n<pre><code>int i = 3;\nDouble d = i * 1.0;\n\nd is 3.0 now.\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
