      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "A fractional suffix <code>.0</code> is generally clearer for the humans. <code>d</code> is the next best option. I would consider <code>D</code> to be harmful as it looks too much like a digit to be adjacent to digits."
